'''Fijit Friends''' were a toy directed toward girls created by [[Mattel]]<ref>[http://blog.babygizmo.com/2011/09/baby-gizmo-spotlight-review-fijit-friends/ Review by Baby Gizmo]</ref>, [[Radica Games]] and [[Girl Tech]]. They made their debut in July 2011 at the [[New York Toy Fair]] and are similar to the famous toy [[Furby]]. Their names are Logan (Voiced by [[Taylor Hawn]]) (blue, sporty), Serafina (Voiced by [[Cassandra Lee Morris]]) (pink, sweetie-pie), Willa (Voiced by [[Sirena Irwin]]) (purple, trend-setting) and Sage (Voiced by [[Brianne Brozey]]) (green, adventurous).<ref>{{cite news|title=Hottest holiday toys for 2011: Fijit Friend|url=http://www.ctpost.com/news/slideshow/Hottest-holiday-toys-for-2011-30996.php#photo-1617398|accessdate=1 September 2013|newspaper=Connecticut Post}}</ref> As of 2016, it seems as if the line has been discontinued, as no new products have been released since 2013. The former web address redirects to mattel’s Customer service website.
Additional releases in the line are Fijit Newbies,<ref>[http://www.timetoplaymag.com/toys/3301/mattel/fijit-friends-newbies/ Newbies at Time to Play]</ref> Fijit Yippits, and Shimmies.<ref>[http://www.timetoplaymag.com/toys/4385/mattel/fijit-friends-yippits/ Yippits at time to Play]</ref> Fijit Friends and Newbies interact with each other and Yippits can learn tricks, and make a yap or bark sound similar to a small dog.<ref>{{cite web|title=Fijit Friends: Home|url=http://www.fijitfriends.com|work=Mattel|publisher=fijitfriends.com|accessdate=26 August 2013}}</ref> A new toy has been released to the family, the Shimmies, which first came out in 2013.
==Awards== In 2012, the Fijit Friends Interactive Figures was awarded "Girl Toy of the Year" title at the 12th Annual Toy of the Year Awards,<ref>{{cite web|title=Toy Of The Year Award Winners – TOTY 2012|url=http://www.thehottoys.com/2012/06/toy-of-the-year-award-winners-toty-2012/|work=TheHotToys|publisher=TheHotToys.com|accessdate=26 August 2013}}</ref> which is held at the American International Toy Fair in New York City.
