==1985 Event - June 28–30, 1985== The 1985 Video Game Masters Tournament was conducted as a fundraiser to raise donations for CARE. The fundraiser set aside half of all entry fees for the CARE/Twin Galaxies African Relief Fund.<ref name="twingalaxies.com"/><ref>"[http://www.twingalaxies.com/index.aspx?c=18&id=1057 Industry Sponsors Ethiopian Fund] {{dead link|date=September 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}" ''[[Play Meter|Play Meter Magazine]]'', New Orleans, LA. May 1, 1985.</ref><ref>[http://www.twingalaxies.com/index.aspx?c=18&id=451 Twin Galaxies Sets 3rd Video masters Tournament - RePlay Magazine, Los Angeles, CA - April 1, 1985] {{dead link|date=September 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>
